'''楓丹白露拉斯維加斯'''（Fontainebleau Las Vegas），2018-2021年名为'''德鲁拉斯维加斯'''（The Drew Las Vegas），是一個位於[[美國|美國]][[內華達州|內華達州]][[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]][[賭城大道|賭城大道]]上未完成的[[酒店|酒店]][[賭場|賭場]]開發案，其68層樓的主體大樓樓高224公尺，是拉斯維加斯第二高的摩天大樓。開發案佔地{{convert|24.5|acre|ha}}，曾預定成為1950年代知名的[[楓丹白露邁阿密海灘|楓丹白露邁阿密海灘]]（Fontainebleau Miami Beach）之姐妹酒店。

開發案預計包含{{convert|95000|sqft}}的賭場、{{convert|60000|sqft}}的水療空間、一座3,300席的表演藝術劇院、1,018間分契式飯店公寓、 {{convert|180000|sqft}}的零售空間、{{convert|400000|sqft}}的室內外會展中心、夜總會，以及24間餐廳和酒吧<ref>{{cite web | author= | title=Fontainblue | url=http://www.vegastodayandtomorrow.com/fontainebleau.htm | work=Vegas Today and Tomorrow | date=2010-09-29 | accessdate=2011-08-29 | archive-date=2021-02-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218183605/http://www.vegastodayandtomorrow.com/fontainebleau.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。開發案在2007年4月30日破土動工，主體建築結構在2008年11月[[封頂|封頂]]。

== 開發案歷史 ==
[[楓丹白露度假村|楓丹白露度假村]]（Fontainebleau Resorts）在2005年售予[[美高梅國際酒店集團|美高梅國際酒店集團]]，在出售前，時任楓丹白露度假村執行長的格蘭·史凱弗（Glenn Schaeffer）曾為度假村創造營收新高。但史凱弗在2009年5月無預警的離開楓丹白露<ref>{{cite news | author=Liz Benston | title=Outlook for Fontainebleau slides from bad to worse | url=http://www.lasvegassun.com/news/2009/jun/08/fontainebleaus-outlook-slides-bad-worse/ | work=The Las Vegas Sun | date=2009-06-08 | accessdate=2011-08-29 | archive-date=2019-10-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022100618/https://lasvegassun.com/news/2009/jun/08/fontainebleaus-outlook-slides-bad-worse/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。史凱弗是楓丹白露拉斯維加斯30億美元借貸案的主要負責人。

=== 破產 ===
在史凱弗離職後，楓丹白露拉斯維加斯的主要貸款銀行[[美國銀行|美國銀行]]拒絕提供資金，使得開發商楓丹白露拉斯維加斯公司（Fontainebleau Las Vegas LLC）在2009年6月宣告破產<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/06/10/fontainebleaulasvegas-idUSBNG42415320090610 |title=Fontainebleau Las Vegas files for Ch. 11 bankruptcy |work=Reuters |date=2009-06-10 |accessdate=2011-08-29 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924142240/http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/06/10/fontainebleaulasvegas-idUSBNG42415320090610 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。楓丹白露的總承包商隨後對楓丹白露拉斯維加斯提出告訴，但兩間公司的持有人實際上同為傑弗瑞·索弗（Jeffrey Soffer）。索弗這項自己控告自己的舉動被認為是希望能迫使銀行提供貸款<ref>{{cite news | author=Arnold M. Knightly | title=Fontainebleau owner suing ... err, himself? | url=http://www.lvrj.com/business/51091292.html | work=The Las Vegas Review-Journal | date=2009-07-18 | accessdate=2011-08-29 | archive-date=2012-10-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001171631/http://www.lvrj.com/business/51091292.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author=Staff writers | title=Court ruling delayed in Fontainebleau bankruptcy dispute | url=http://www.lvrj.com/business/53787037.html | work=The Las Vegas Review-Journal | date=2009-08-20 | accessdate=2011-08-29 | archive-date=2012-10-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001172327/http://www.lvrj.com/business/53787037.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。開發案在約進行至約七成左右進度時停工，楓丹白露拉斯維加斯原本預計在2009年10月開幕。2009年7月，楓丹白露在破產法庭上獲准提前中止作為員工招募中心的辦公室租約，也獲准取消原本已排定在2010年前半取行的活動企劃<ref>{{cite news | author=Steve Green | url=http://www.lasvegassun.com/news/2009/jul/17/fontainebleau-moves-cancel-conventions-worker-cont/ | title=Fontainebleau moves to cancel conventions, worker contracts | work=The Las Vegas Sun | date=2009-07-17 | accessdate=2011-08-29 | archive-date=2019-09-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190921201746/https://lasvegassun.com/news/2009/jul/17/fontainebleau-moves-cancel-conventions-worker-cont/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年10月，[[Penn_National_Gaming|Penn National Gaming]]考慮以3億美元購買已部分完工的度假村和其{{convert|24.5|acre|ha}}的土地，平均每英畝土地的價格為1,200萬美元，而在當時兩年前賭城大道的土地每英畝開價超過3,000萬美元。此外主建築的建造費用至停工時已耗資20億美元<ref>{{cite news |author=Howard Stutz |url=http://www.lvrj.com/business/penn-makes-strip-pitch-63659662.html#blogcomments?submitted=y |title=Penn makes Strip pitch; Gaming company begins the bidding on Fontainebleau |work=The Las Vegas Review-Journal |date=2009-08-20 |accessdate=2011-08-29 |archive-date=2012-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121002054524/http://www.lvrj.com/business/penn-makes-strip-pitch-63659662.html#blogcomments?submitted=y |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 收購 ===
2009年11月23日在[[佛羅里達州|佛州]][[邁阿密|邁阿密]]舉行的破產法庭上，企業融資家卡爾·艾康（Carl Icahn）以1.56億美元擊敗Penn National Gaming贏得競標，取得楓丹白露拉斯維加斯的控制權。<ref>{{cite news | author=Arnold M. Knightly | title=Icahn wins auction to buy Fontainebleau for $150 million | url=http://www.lvrj.com/news/breaking_news/Icahn-82795542.html | work=The Las Vegas Review-Journal | date=2010-01-27 | accessdate=2011-08-29 | archive-date=2012-06-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120606160722/http://www.lvrj.com/news/breaking_news/Icahn-82795542.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>艾康的資金中包含5,100萬美元的破产保护企业（debtor-in-possession）貸款資金，可在度假村實際售出錢提供建物維護、員工薪水、其他開支，也免除了每週需要招開破產法庭來借貸或使用資金的麻煩。Penn National Gaming最高出價為1.45億美元。

截至2009年11月，繼續完成度假村開發案所需的資金估計為10至15億美元<ref name=lvs20091123>{{cite news | author=Steve Green | title=Carl Icahn offers $156 million for Fontainebleau, outbids Penn National | url=http://www.lasvegassun.com/news/2009/nov/23/carl-icahn-offers-136-million-fontainebleau/ | work=The Las Vegas Sun | date=2009-11-23 | accessdate=2011-08-29 | archive-date=2018-07-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719143436/https://lasvegassun.com/news/2009/nov/23/carl-icahn-offers-136-million-fontainebleau/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年2月8日，在沒有其他後續競標者的情況下，卡爾·艾康取得了開發案的部分持有權，支付了1.5億美元。

2010年10月，艾康出售了原本預計供酒店使用的傢俱和其他物件，包括地毯、床墊、各式傢俱等。關於拉斯維加斯楓丹白露度假村未來的計劃尚未對外公開<ref>{{cite news | author=Steve Friess | title=For many, gamble lost in once-booming Las Vegas | url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hhtnUkzqDzqdU2kllH-xVoPmnHnQ?docId=CNG.55c503ebe84a0eea27eb368cc04917d2.81 | work=Agence France Presse | date=2010-10-21 | accessdate=2011-08-29 | archive-date=2010-10-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101026180104/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hhtnUkzqDzqdU2kllH-xVoPmnHnQ?docId=CNG.55c503ebe84a0eea27eb368cc04917d2.81 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 再次转手 ===
2017年8月，投资公司威科夫集团（Witkoff Group）和New Valley LLC以6亿美元联合收购了该项目<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fontainebleau on Las Vegas Strip sells for $600M|url=https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/fontainebleau-on-las-vegas-strip-sells-for-600m/|work=Las Vegas Review-Journal|date=2017-08-29|accessdate=2019-04-25|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112225045/https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/fontainebleau-on-las-vegas-strip-sells-for-600m/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年2月12日，威科夫集团宣布和[[萬豪國際|萬豪國際集團]]合作，项目改名为德鲁拉斯维加斯（The Drew Las Vegas），预计在2020年底前开业<ref name="NewName">{{Cite web|title=Fontainebleau on Las Vegas Strip has new name and opening date|url=https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/fontainebleau-on-las-vegas-strip-has-new-name-and-opening-date/|work=Las Vegas Review-Journal|date=2018-02-12|accessdate=2019-04-25|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031081957/https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/fontainebleau-on-las-vegas-strip-has-new-name-and-opening-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。项目的新名称部分是为了纪念威科夫集团拥有者{{le|史蒂夫·威科夫|Steve Witkoff}}的已故22岁儿子安德鲁·威科夫（Andrew Witkoff），他在2011年因过量服用{{le|羟考酮|Oxycodone}}而死亡<ref name="NewName"/>。

2019年4月，威科夫宣布开业时间将延迟到2022年第二季度以更好地确定建筑预算，他同时宣布，为了纪念他的儿子，度假村的大部分利润将用于旨在打击毒品成瘾的家族基金会<ref>{{Cite news|title=Vegas Strip’s $3.1 Billion Resort Postponed More Than a Year|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-04-16/vegas-strip-s-3-1-billion-resort-to-be-delayed-more-than-a-year|date=2019-04-24|accessdate=2019-04-25|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213220754/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-04-16/vegas-strip-s-3-1-billion-resort-to-be-delayed-more-than-a-year|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年3月，建设工作因[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]疫情而暂停<ref>{{cite news |last=Segall |first=Eli |title=Drew Las Vegas on hold, other construction continues amid virus' spread |url=https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/drew-las-vegas-on-hold-other-construction-continues-amid-virus-spread-1985449/ |access-date=2021-02-13 |work=Las Vegas Review-Journal |date=2020-03-18 |archive-date=2021-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210718150231/https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/drew-las-vegas-on-hold-other-construction-continues-amid-virus-spread-1985449/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。几个月后，承包商因未付款项向法院申请总额达数百万美元的留置令<ref>{{cite news |last=Segall |first=Eli |title=Contractors say they're owed $36M for work done at Drew Las Vegas |url=https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/contractors-say-theyre-owed-36m-for-work-done-at-drew-las-vegas-2054203/ |access-date=2021-03-09 |work=Las Vegas Review-Journal |date=2020-06-16 |archive-date=2021-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716134917/https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/contractors-say-theyre-owed-36m-for-work-done-at-drew-las-vegas-2054203/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，最近加入项目的高管在疫情期间被解雇后起诉开发商未付工资，声称他们的雇员合同遭到违约<ref>{{cite news |last=Segall |first=Eli |title=Laid-off Drew Las Vegas staffers sue owner, claim money owed |url=https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/laid-off-drew-las-vegas-staffers-sue-owner-claim-money-owed-2061041/ |access-date=2021-03-09 |work=Las Vegas Review-Journal |date=2020-06-25 |archive-date=2021-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210719025816/https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/laid-off-drew-las-vegas-staffers-sue-owner-claim-money-owed-2061041/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 回归枫丹白露 ===
2021年2月，杰弗瑞·索弗通过他在佛罗里达的公司枫丹白露发展（Fontainebleau Development）联合[[科氏工業集團|科氏工业]]买回了此项目，并正在考虑已建成75%的该物业的未来发展<ref>{{cite news |last=Horwath |first=Bryan |title=Firm acquires Drew Las Vegas with plans to finish stalled resort project |url=https://lasvegassun.com/news/2021/feb/12/firm-acquires-drew-las-vegas-with-plans-to-finish/ |access-date=2021-02-13 |work=Las Vegas Sun |date=2021-02-12 |archive-date=2021-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215211819/https://lasvegassun.com/news/2021/feb/12/firm-acquires-drew-las-vegas-with-plans-to-finish/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Koch>{{cite news |last=Segall |first=Eli |title=Koch Industries teams with developer to buy Drew on Las Vegas Strip |url=https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/koch-industries-teams-with-developer-to-buy-drew-on-las-vegas-strip-2278674/ |access-date=2021-02-13 |work=Las Vegas Review-Journal |date=2021-02-11 |archive-date=2021-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716134912/https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/koch-industries-teams-with-developer-to-buy-drew-on-las-vegas-strip-2278674/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Gittelsohn |first=John |last2=Palmeri |first2=Christopher |title=Koch Industries Buys Stalled Las Vegas Casino Development |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-11/koch-industries-buys-75-stake-in-stalled-vegas-casino-project |access-date=2021-02-13 |work=Bloomberg |date=2021-02-12 |archive-date=2021-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716150518/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-11/koch-industries-buys-75-stake-in-stalled-vegas-casino-project |dead-url=no }}</ref>。尽管所有权发生变化，万豪仍参与该项目<ref>{{cite news |last=Segall |first=Eli |title=What's next for Drew property on the Strip a mystery for now |url=https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/business-columns/real-estate-insider/whats-next-for-drew-property-on-the-strip-a-mystery-for-now-2280055/ |access-date=2021-03-09 |work=Las Vegas Review-Journal |date=2021-02-13 |archive-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515215103/https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/business-columns/real-estate-insider/whats-next-for-drew-property-on-the-strip-a-mystery-for-now-2280055/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在收购时，德鲁的物业价值为6.155亿美元<ref>{{cite news |last=Segall |first=Eli |title=New owners landed Drew Las Vegas through 'deed in lieu' |url=https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/new-owners-landed-drew-las-vegas-through-deed-in-lieu-2286833/ |access-date=2021-03-09 |work=Las Vegas Review-Journal |date=2021-02-22 |archive-date=2021-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716134913/https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/new-owners-landed-drew-las-vegas-through-deed-in-lieu-2286833/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年7月，[[萬豪國際|万豪]]宣布酒店部分名为拉斯维加斯大道JW万豪酒店（JW Marriott Las Vegas Blvd），计划2023年10月开业<ref>{{cite news |last=Segall |first=Eli |title=Former Fontainebleau to open in 2023, says Marriott |url=https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/former-fontainebleau-to-open-in-2023-says-marriott-2403802/ |access-date=2021-07-23 |work=Las Vegas Review-Journal |date=2021-07-21 |archive-date=2021-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210805213309/https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/former-fontainebleau-to-open-in-2023-says-marriott-2403802/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Moeller |first1=Joe |last2=Wright |first2=Lucas |title='I think it's a big eyesore': Visitors happy to hear new plans for former Fontainebleu |url=https://www.8newsnow.com/news/the-strip/i-think-its-a-big-eyesore-visitors-happy-to-hear-new-plans-for-former-fontainebleu/ |access-date=2021-07-23 |work=KLAS |date=2021-07-21 |archive-date=2021-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724150608/https://www.8newsnow.com/news/the-strip/i-think-its-a-big-eyesore-visitors-happy-to-hear-new-plans-for-former-fontainebleu/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但万豪在10月宣布退出该项目，由枫丹白露自行经营酒店部分。<ref>{{cite news |last=Segall |first=Eli |title=Marriott exits unfinished former Fontainebleau project |url=https://www.reviewjournal.com/business/casinos-gaming/marriott-cuts-ties-with-unfinished-former-fontainebleau-project-2459629/ |access-date=2021-11-10 |work=Las Vegas Review-Journal |date=2021-10-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Marriott exits Fontainebleau deal |url=https://news3lv.com/news/local/stalled-former-fountainebleu-hits-another-roadblock-marriott-exits-deal |access-date=2021-11-10 |work=KSNV |date=2021-10-14}}</ref>

